description: Demolition of existing dwellings and erection of a mixture of two storey, two storey with roof accommodation and three storey buildings comprising: seventy five 3-bedroomed and eleven 2-bedroomed houses, seventy 2-bedroomed and fifty eight 1-bedroomed self contained flats; provision of cycle and refuse facilities, 269 car parking spaces, alteration to existing and provision of new access.
